    <wave>11</wave>
    <estimated-effort>1-2 hours</estimated-effort>
    <tags>dataverse, deploy, script, wave-11</tags>
    <rigor-level>FULL</rigor-level>
    <rigor-reason>Modifies deployed Dataverse data + creates new .ps1 script; data-modifying task per CLAUDE.md §8 TEST-MODIFYING analog. FULL rigor regardless of step count.</rigor-reason>
